bilingual.target: 导弹系统能够拦截来袭的导弹。
他们在模拟导弹的弹道。

bilingual.source: They are testing a new type of missile.
bilingual.target: 他们正在测试一种新型的导弹。

bilingual.source: An unguided missile can be very dangerous.
bilingual.target: 无指导的导弹可能非常危险。

bilingual.source: The missile travels very fast in the air.
bilingual.target: 导弹在空中飞行时速度非常快。
这个国家拥有先进的导弹技术。

bilingual.source: The missile was equipped with a powerful warhead.
bilingual.target: 导弹配备了一个强大的弹头。

list.abstract: missile /ˈmɪsaɪl/DJ /ˈmɪsl/DJUS /'mɪsḷ/KKUS noun a weapon that is sent through the air and that explodes when it hits the thing that it is aimed at 导弹 nuclear missiles 核导弹 a missile base/site 导弹基地／发射场 an object that is thrown at sb to hurt them 发射物；投掷物 Missiles including stones and bottles were thrown at the police. 包括石头、瓶子之类的东西朝警察扔了过去。
missile中文名为米赛尔，也可直译为导弹。是一家专业生产山地自行车及配件的厂家。

yingyinNormal.en: The program terminal from an ICBM missile...
But that brings us to the elephant in the room. Missile defense.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不过还有一件我们都在考虑的事。导弹防御。

yingyinNormal.en: It was 1987. Separatists had hijacked a Soviet missile silo in Kursk and launched an ICBM at the United States.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那是一九八七年，分裂主义者劫持了苏联位于库尔斯克的导弹发射井，向美国发射了一枚洲际弹道导弹。

yingyinNormal.en: So, the question is: who in S.H.I.E.L.D could launch a domestic missile strike? Pierce.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在的问题是局里谁有权发动国内导弹袭击。皮尔斯。

yingyinNormal.en: That's right. And the missile defense system, too. And I'm prepared to give him both if necessary.
yingyinNormal.zh: 没错，还有拆除导弹防御系统。如果有必要，我两样都会满足他。

yingyinNormal.en: Their instruments won't work up here. Missile tracking won't work. They'll have to fire a line of sight.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在那里仪表会失灵，导弹追踪也不管用，他们只能靠肉眼攻击。

yingyinNormal.en: But I digress. Where was I? Yes. Business is booming, right? A chopper here, a missile there. Guns, whatever.
yingyinNormal.zh: 噢，我跑题了？对了，生意很红火？这儿卖架直升机，那儿卖颗导弹，还有那些枪。

yingyinNormal.en: I knew I had to shrink between the molecules to disarm the missile. But my regulator had sustained too much damage.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我知道我必须缩小到分子状态穿进去，才能拆除导弹，但我的调节器已经遭受了太多损坏。

yingyinNormal.en: A missile hit your engine. And we took it out of you. You're hurt really bad.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一颗飞弹击中你的引擎，我们把它拿了出来，你伤得很重。
